{
  "stem": "25589.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Reason was, we ate, and we couldn't hear the bell.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because maybe he stayed open until about 7:00, 8:00.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And during suppertime, everybody quiet.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Nobody spoke.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "When you're finished and off the table, my dad was downstairs.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We'd go back to-- but we were usually, we were in bed at 7:00.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Up to, I remember, up to the age of 11, 12, 7:00, everybody upstairs.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And that's the way we were brought up, very strict.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Maybe we benefited from it, as today, we benefit by the way we were brought up.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And like I said, there were no favors.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Yeah, I think my dad favored my sister.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I always thought that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And you know, well, she was a girl.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "It was the only girl between the four guys, you know, or the five guys.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So I'm sure they favored her.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And like I said, my mother always thought the way you dress your children, that's the way people treat you.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "If they look well, they treat you well.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And it's a true thing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And my favorite pastime was, in those days, go to Amsterdam to see my family.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And I didn't wait for nobody.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I was eight, nine years old.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I put myself on the train and go.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And then I knew my father and mother would, they were going to come in the afternoon.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "But I didn't care.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "I go by myself.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, I had a cousin.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "His name was also Jonas, and he was like a brother to me.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We used to do everything.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I'd go there and get off the train.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And there was a-- I knew which bus to take to get to where they were.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was not a bus, streetcar.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I knew it-- number nine.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "See, I remember number nine.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
